                <h1 style="text-decoration: underline" class="whitefont">Lifestyle</h1>
                <h4 class="whitefont">The best lifestyle advice is: Be good! Be good for your health, and be good for the uplift of the world. The suggestions below are meant as things to think about as you deepen your practice or if you feel you need a change in your habits to be in line with this advice. Lifestyle changes should be small and gradual so they stick.</h4>
                <h3 class="whitefont">Quitting everything</h3>
                <h4 class="whitefont">Don’t do it! Change one thing a time. Start with adding your practice. Make it a habit. Then, to support your practice, change one small thing if you like. Make that a habit. Small changes over time are much better than massive changes all at once.</h4>
              </div>
            </div>
